commit.message: Make it possible to parse ping timeouts includes timestamps: #37
Add -O option to ping execution when --timestamp option is specified on Linux
Set default serializer for timestamps of ICMP replies
Modify to support isort 5.0.0 or later
Add an option for pytest-md-report to CI
